Name: Odin
Line: [voice over] Long before the birth of light there was darkness, and from that darkness, came the Dark Elves. Millennia ago, the most ruthless of their kind, Malekith, sought to transform our universe back into one of eternal night.

Name: Odin
Line: Such evil was possible through the power of the Aether, an ancient force of infinite destruction.

Name: Odin
Line: The noble armies of Asgard, led by my father, King Bor, waged a mighty war against these creatures.

Name: Malekith
Line: Send the Kursed.

Name: Odin
Line: As the Nine Worlds converged above him, Malekith could at last unleash the Aether...

Name: Odin
Line: But Asgard ripped the weapon from his grasp. Without it, the Dark Elves fell. With the battle all but lost, Malekith sacrificed his own people in a desperate attempt to lay waste to Asgard's army.

Name: Malekith
Line: [subtitled] Their deaths will mean our survival. This war is far from over.

Name: Odin
Line: Malekith was vanquished, and the Aether was no more. Or so we were led to believe.

Name: Frigga
Line: Loki.

Name: Loki
Line: Hello, mother. Have I made you proud?

Name: Frigga
Line: Please, don't make this worse.

Name: Loki
Line: Define worse.

Name: Odin
Line: Enough! I will speak to the prisoner alone.

Name: Loki
Line: [laughs] I really don't see what all the fuss is about.

Name: Odin
Line: Do you not truly feel the gravity of your crimes? Wherever you go there is war, ruin and death.

Name: Loki
Line: I went down to Midgard to rule the people of Earth as a benevolent god. Just like you.

Name: Odin
Line: We are not gods. We are born, we live, we die. Just as humans do.

Name: Loki
Line: Give or take 5000 years.

Name: Odin
Line: All this because Loki desires a throne.

Name: Loki
Line: It is my birthright.

Name: Odin
Line: Your birthright was to die as a child. Cast out onto a frozen rock. If I had not taken you in you would not be here now to hate me.

Name: Loki
Line: If I am for the axe, then for mercy's sake, just swing it. It's not that I don't love our little talks, it's just ... I don't love them.

Name: Odin
Line: Frigga is the only reason you are still alive and you will never see her again. You will spend the rest of your days in the dungeons.

Name: Loki
Line: And what of Thor? You'll make that witless oaf king while I rot in chains?

Name: Odin
Line: Thor must strife to undo the damage you have done. He will bring order to the nine realms and then, yes. He will be king.

Name: Sif
Line: I've got this completely under control!

Name: Thor
Line: Is that why everything is on fire?

Name: Sif
Line: You're welcome. [a Kronan arrives] All yours.

Name: Thor
Line: Hello. [the Kronan growls] I accept your surrender.

Name: Thor
Line: Anyone else?

Name: Thor
Line: Hogun, the peace is nearly won across the Nine Realms. You should stay here. Be with your people, where your heart is. Asgard can wait.

Name: Thor
Line: As you have mine. Heimdall, when you're ready.

Name: Odin
Line: Is Vanaheim secure?

Name: Thor
Line: As are Nornheim and Ria. Though our work would have gone more quickly with you at the fore.

Name: Odin
Line: You must think I'm a piece of bread that needs to be buttered so heavily.

Name: Thor
Line: That was not my intent.

Name: Odin
Line: For the first time since the Bifrost was destroyed, the Nine Realms are at peace. They're well reminded of our strength and you have earned their respect and my gratitude.

Name: Thor
Line: Thank you.

Name: Odin
Line: Nothing out of order except your confused and distracted heart.

Name: Thor
Line: This isn't about Jane Foster, Father.

Name: Odin
Line: Human lives are fleeting, they are nothing. You'd be better served by what lies in front of you [Camera briefly turns to Sif] I'm telling you this not as the all-father but as your father. You are ready. The time has come for you to take the throne. Embrace and celebrate what you've won. Join your warriors. Eat and drink, revel in their celebration. At least pretend to enjoy yourself.

Name: Sif
Line: There was a time you would celebrate for weeks.

Name: Thor
Line: I remember you celebrated the battle of Haragon so much that you nearly started a second.

Name: Sif
Line: Well, the first was so much fun.

Name: Sif
Line: Take a drink with me. Surely the All-Father could have no further task for you tonight.

Name: Thor
Line: No, this is one I set myself.

Name: Sif
Line: It has not gone unnoticed that you disappear each night. There are Nine Realms. Future king of Asgard must focus on more than one.

Name: Thor
Line: I thank you for your sword and for your counsel, good Lady Sif.

Name: Richard
Line: Hi.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Hi.

Name: Richard
Line: So what's the story with you?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Why does there have to be a story, there's no story.

Name: Richard
Line: You've spent the first ten minutes of our date hiding behind a menu that has three choices on it. It's either chicken, vegetarian or fish, Jane. I think there's a story and I'm thinking the story involves a guy?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: It's complicated.

Name: Richard
Line: Is he still around?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: No, he...went away.

Name: Richard
Line: I've been there. The going away, it's hard. I'd been seeing a woman and uh...she took a job in New York, eventually the distance killed it. And...and the fact that she uh...she kept sleeping with other dudes.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: No!

Name: Richard
Line: Oh, so many.

Name: Richard
Line: Hi. Um...could we get some wine please?

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Sure, I'd love some.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Richard, this is Darcy. [to Darcy] What are you doing here?

Name: Richard
Line: Oh, hello.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: So, I show up to work at the lab-slash-your mom's house, fully expecting you to be moping around in your pajamas eating ice cream obsessing about you know who...

Name: Richard
Line: Ah.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: But you're not! You're wearing lady clothes, you even showered, didn't you? You smell good.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Is there a point to all this, cause there really has to be a point to all this.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Right. You know that scientific equipment you don't look at anymore? You might wanna start looking at it now

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: This is the reason we came all the way out here.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: It's malfunctioning.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: That's what I said.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: That's what I did! But you just hit a little more scientific.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: I'm sure it's nothing.

Name: Richard
Line: Yeah.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: It didn't look like nothing. Kind of looks like the readings that Erik was rambling about. [to Richard] Our friend Erik, kind of went banana-balls.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: He's not interested. I'm not interested. Time for you to go now.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Okay.

Name: Richard
Line: Short but sweet.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: She needs help.

Name: Richard
Line: I think I'm gonna have the sea bass.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Sea bass. Yeah, sea bass is good.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Sea bass, sea bass, sea bass, sea bass, sea bass, sea bass, sea bass...sea bass. Sea bass...

Name: Richard
Line: Jane, maybe you should stop saying sea bass and go out to your friend.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: This was so fun.

Name: Richard
Line: You know, I'll just stay here and say sea bass alone.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: And I hate you.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: What?! I thought he was cute.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Just shut up and drive.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Who's he?

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: He's my intern.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: You have an intern?

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Oh, yeah.

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: Hello, Dr. Foster. It's uh...it's a great honor to be working with you.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Right. I have to call Erik.

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: Oh, uh...take a right.

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: Left!

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: I have totally mastered driving in London.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Hi, Erik, it's me again. Where are you? I came here because you said you were onto something and then vanished.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Come on, this is exciting! Look, the intern is excited.

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: Ian.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Do you want the phase meter?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: No.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: [to Ian] Bring the phase meter.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: The toaster looking thing.

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: I know what the phase meter is.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: How do I change the ring tone on this thing?

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: An Astrophysicist with three degrees should be able to change her own ring tone.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Why are you calling me?

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: I didn't want to shout. [to Ian, who's following behind her] Intern, the entrance is this way.

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: Ian. My name's Ian.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: I am not getting stabbed in the name of science.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: It's okay, we're Americans!

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Is that supposed to make them like us?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Oh, they're kids.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: No, we're scientists. Well, I am.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Thanks.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Can you show us?

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: That doesn't seem rigged.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Where did it go?

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: That's...that's incredible.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: What happened?

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: I want to throw something. Jane, give me your shoe.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: I haven't seen readings like this since...

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: New Mexico?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Don't touch anything!

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: [to Ian] Give me your shoe.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Where those the car keys?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Darcy!

Name: Malekith
Line: [subtitled] The Aether awakens us. The Convergence returns.

Name: Heimdall
Line: You're late.

Name: Thor
Line: Merriment can sometimes be a heavier burden than battle.

Name: Heimdall
Line: Then you're doing one of them incorrectly.

Name: Thor
Line: Perhaps. How fare the stars?

Name: Heimdall
Line: Still shining. From here I can see Nine Realms and ten trillion souls.

Name: Heimdall
Line: You recall what I told you of the Convergence?

Name: Thor
Line: Yes, the alignment of the worlds. It approaches, doesn't it?

Name: Heimdall
Line: The universe hasn't seen this marvel since before my watch began. Few can sense, even fewer can see it. A world that's infected can be dangerous. It is truly beautiful.

Name: Thor
Line: I see nothing.

Name: Heimdall
Line: Or perhaps that is not the beauty you seek.

Name: Thor
Line: How is she?

Name: Heimdall
Line: She's quite clever, your mortal. She doesn't know it yet, but she studies the Convergence as well. Even...

Name: Thor
Line: What?

Name: Heimdall
Line: I can't see her.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Jane! Where the hell were you?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Tell me you didn't call the police!

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: What was I supposed to do?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Not call the police!

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: I was freaking out.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: You call the cops they tell the feds, the next thing you know we have SHIELD crawling all over area fifty-one-ing the place.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Jane!

Name: Jane Foster
Line: We had a stable gratification anomaly, we had unheeded access. Our only competition was ten years old!

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Jane, you were gone for five hours!

Name: Jane Foster
Line: What? [suddenly the weather turns, it starts raining and they hear the sound of thunder, Jane looks around her and puts her hand out]

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: That's weird. [they see it's raining but it's not raining on Jane and Darcy, there's an invisible barrier protecting them, suddenly Jane sees Thor standing a few feet away from them, Jane hands her gadget to Darcy and walks towards Thor, as she walks away the invisible barrier follows her and the rain starts falling on Darcy] Typical. [as Jane walks towards Thor]

Name: Thor
Line: Jane. [as she reaches him suddenly she slaps him hard in the face]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Sorry. I just needed to make sure you were real, it's been a very strange day.

Name: Thor
Line: Well, I am. Jane... [suddenly she slaps him again]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Where were you?!

Name: Thor
Line: Where were you? Heimdall could not see you.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: I was right here where you left me. I was waiting and then I was crying and then I went out looking for you. You said you were coming back

Name: Thor
Line: I know, I know, but the Bifrost was destroyed. The Nine Realms erupted into chaos, wars were raging, marauding hordes were pillaging. I had to put an end to the slaughter.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: As excuses go, that's not terrible. But I saw you on TV, you were...you were in New York!

Name: Thor
Line: Jane, I fought to protect you from the dangers of my world, but I was wrong, I was a fool. [Thor places his hand Jane's face] I believe that fate brought us together. Jane, I don't know where you were or what happened, but I do know this.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: What?

Name: Thor
Line: I know...

Name: Jane Foster
Line: You do?

Name: Thor
Line: Do what? [they lean in close and just as they are about to kiss Darcy interrupts them; referring to the rain]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Hey! Is that you? [Thor looks up and the rain stops]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Uh...we're kind of in the middle of something.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Um...I'm pretty sure we are getting arrested.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: [to Thor] Hold that thought. [she turns and runs towards the police]

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Look at you, still all muscly and everything. How's space?

Name: Thor
Line: Space is fine. [Jane walks over to the police]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Excuse me?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Yes.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: He's my intern. My intern's intern.

Name: Thor
Line: Jane! Jane? [he helps her stand] You alright?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: What just happened? [the other police officer approaches Jane apprehensively]

Name: Thor
Line: The woman is unwell.

Name: Thor
Line: So am I. [talking into his radio]

Name: Thor
Line: Hold on to me.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: What are you doing? [suddenly the Bifrost opens and Thor takes Jane to Asgard; Darcy looks up as they disappear]

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Holy shit! [Thor and Jane travel through the Bifrost and enter Asgard where Heimdall is guarding as always, Jane looks around her in amazement]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: We have to do that again. [she notices Heimdall for the first time] Hi.

Name: Heimdall
Line: Welcome to Asgard. [returning to their homeland, Svartalfheim, Malekith kneels and grabs a handful of dust from the ground]

Name: Malekith
Line: [subtitled] Look at my legacy, Algrim. I barely remember the time before light. [Algrim places his hand on Malekith's shoulder]

Name: Malekith
Line: [subtitled] The Asgardians will suffer as we have suffered. I will reclaim the Aether. I will restore our world and I'll put an end to this poisonous world. [as the Asgardian physicians study Jane and the force within her]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: What's that?

Name: Thor
Line: This is not of Earth, what is it?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: That's a quantum field generator, isn't it?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Does a Soul Forge transfer molecular energy from one place to another? [Eir looks impressed]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: It's a quantum field generator. [Thor smiles at her] [Odin enters the room as the Thor looks on to Jane as she is being examined]

Name: Odin
Line: My words are mere noises to you that you ignore them completely?

Name: Thor
Line: She's ill.

Name: Odin
Line: She is mortal. Illness is their defining trait.

Name: Thor
Line: I brought here because we can help her.

Name: Odin
Line: She does not belong here in Asgard anymore than a goat belongs at a banquet table. [Jane sits up and looks at Thor]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Did he just...? [to Odin] Who do you think you are?

Name: Odin
Line: I'm Odin. King of Asgard. Protector of the Nine Realms.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Oh. Well, I'm...

Name: Odin
Line: I know very well who you are, Jane Foster. [Jane turns to look at Thor]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: You told your Dad about me?

Name: Thor
Line: Something is within her, father, something I have not seen before.

Name: Odin
Line: Her world has its healers, their called doctors, let them deal with it. Guards, take her back to Midgard. [as two guards approach Jane and go to grab her, suddenly the energy force within her sets off again throwing the two guards aside]

Name: Thor
Line: Don't touch her. [he leans down and tenderly touches Jane] Jane, are you alright? [Jane nods her head, Odin inspects the energy force running through Jane's body and realizes it's the Aether]

Name: Odin
Line: That's impossible.

Name: Thor
Line: No, it's defending itself.

Name: Odin
Line: Come with me. There are relics that predate the universe itself. What lies within her appears to be one of them. The Nine Realms are not eternal. They had a dawn as they will have a dusk. [Odin shows Thor and Jane an ancient book] But before that dawn the dark forces, the Dark Elves, reigned absolute and unchallenged.

Name: Thor
Line: [reading from the book] "Born of eternal night, the Dark Elves comes to steal away your light." They were these stories mother told us as children.

Name: Odin
Line: Their leader, Malekith made a weapon out of that darkness, it was called the Aether. While the other relics often appeared as stones, the Aether is fluid and ever changing. It changes matter into dark matter and seeks out to host bodies, drawing strength from their life force. Malekith sought to use the Aether's power to return the universe to one of darkness. But after eternities of blood shed, my father Bor, finally triumphed, ushering in the peace that lasted thousands of years.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: What happened?

Name: Odin
Line: He killed them all.

Name: Thor
Line: Are you certain? The Aether was said to have been destroyed with them and yet here it is.

Name: Odin
Line: The Dark Elves are dead.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Does your book happen to mention how to get it out of me?

Name: Odin
Line: No, it does not. [back on Svartalfheim, in his ship Malekith plots his vengeance against the Asgardians]

Name: Malekith
Line: [subtitled] The Realms will be aligned soon. [Malekith takes out a knife and turns to Algrim]

Name: Malekith
Line: [subtitled] You'll be the last of the Kursed. [Malekith stabs Algrim in the stomach with his knife]

Name: Malekith
Line: [subtitled] You will become darkness, doomed to this existence until it consumes you. [one of the dark elves places a molten rock in Malekith's hand and Malekith places it inside Algrim's stomach] And then no power of our enemies will stop me.

Name: Loki
Line: Odin continues to bring me new friends. How thoughtful.

Name: Frigga
Line: The books I sent, do they not interest you? [Loki turns and we see Frigga is in Loki's cell]

Name: Loki
Line: Is that how I'm to while away eternity, reading?

Name: Frigga
Line: I've done everything in my power to make you comfortable, Loki.

Name: Loki
Line: Have you? Does Odin share your concern? Does Thor? It must be so inconvenient them asking after me day and night.

Name: Frigga
Line: You know full well it was your actions that brought you here.

Name: Loki
Line: My actions. I was merely giving truth to the lie that I had been fed my entire life, that I was born to be a king.

Name: Frigga
Line: A king? A true king admits his faults. What of the lives you took on Earth?

Name: Loki
Line: A mere handful compared to the number that Odin has taken himself.

Name: Frigga
Line: Your father...

Name: Loki
Line: [shouts] He's not my father!

Name: Frigga
Line: Then am I not your mother? [Loki hesitates for a moment]

Name: Loki
Line: You're not. [Frigga smiles at him with tears in her eyes]

Name: Frigga
Line: Always so perceptive about everyone but yourself. [she takes a step towards him and extends her hands, Loki goes to touch her hand but his hand goes through hers and we see that she's a hologram, Loki looks at Frigga with sadness and her hologram disappears] [Jane and Thor walk in Asgard]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: When you came for me, you knew I was in trouble.

Name: Thor
Line: Well Heimdall had lost sight of you, you were no longer on Earth.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Well, how's that possible?

Name: Thor
Line: I believe you were in between worlds. The Nine Realms travel within Yggdrasil, orbiting Midgard in much the way your planet orbits the sun. Every five thousand years the worlds align perfectly, we call this the Convergence. [he takes her hand and he shows her by touching his palm to hers] During this time the boarders between worlds become blurred. It's possible you found one of these points. We are lucky that it remained open. Once the worlds pass out of alignment, the connection is lost. [he leans closer and they kiss]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: I liked the way you explained that. What's gonna happen to me?

Name: Thor
Line: I'll find a way to save you, Jane.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Your father said there was...

Name: Thor
Line: My father doesn't know everything. [suddenly they are interrupted by Frigga]

Name: Frigga
Line: Don't let him hear you say that.

Name: Thor
Line: Jane Foster, please meet Frigga, the Queen of Asgard, my mother. [Jane looking embarrassed quickly removes her hand from Thor's mother, Frigga]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Hi. [in his cell, Algrim pulls out the rock that Malekith had placed in his stomach, he crushes it in his hand, transforming himself into a Kursed, he breaks free and releases the other prisoners, Loki watches all this from his cell, then Algrim walks up to Loki's cell and he look at Loki for a moment before turning and walking away]

Name: Loki
Line: You might want to take the stairs to the left. [Algrim turns and looks at Loki before walking away again; outside they hear the prison alarm going off]

Name: Frigga
Line: The prisons.

Name: Thor
Line: Loki.

Name: Frigga
Line: [referring to Jane] Go, I will look after her. [Thor takes off with his hammer; in the prison Volstagg and Fandral enter the fight with the prisoners]

Name: Thor
Line: Return to your cells and further harm will come to you. You have my word. [suddenly one of the prisoners punches him in the face] Very well, you don't have my word. [Thor punches him back and starts fighting with the other prisoners]

Name: Odin
Line: [to his guards] Send a squadron to the weapons vault, defend it at all costs. Seal the dungeon.

Name: Frigga
Line: Odin.

Name: Odin
Line: Frigga. [to the Asgardian guards] Go! [to Frigga and Jane] It's a skirmish, nothing to fear.

Name: Frigga
Line: You've never been a very good liar. [at that moment Jane notices Sif as she walks past them]

Name: Odin
Line: Take her to you chambers, I'll come for you when it's safe.

Name: Frigga
Line: You take care.

Name: Odin
Line: Despite all I have survived, my queen still worries over me.

Name: Frigga
Line: It's only because I worry over you that you have survived. [Odin goes off, Frigga leads Jane away, she takes a sword from one of the guards] Listen to me now, I need you to do everything I ask and no questions.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Yes, ma'am. [as Heimdall is stood in his usual guarding post, he suddenly hears something turns and runs out onto the Bifrost Bridge, he jumps onto one of Malekith's ships cloaked in invisibility, making it visible and manages to send it crashing into the sea, but he soon finds that a giant ship is behind him releasing smaller ships to attack Asgard, Heimdall activates a shield to protect Asgard but Algrim manages to deactivate it sending a ship to crash into the palace] [after Malekith's ship has crashed into the palace the Dark Elves start attacking the Asgardian soldiers killing them all, Malekith leaves the ship and goes to look for Frigga and Jane after which Odin arrives to find all the soldiers killed]

Name: Odin
Line: Frigga. [Malekith finds the tower where Frigga is hiding Jane and enters the room]

Name: Frigga
Line: Stand down, creature. You may still survive this.

Name: Malekith
Line: I have survived worse, woman.

Name: Frigga
Line: Who are you?

Name: Malekith
Line: I am Malekith, and I would have what it is mine. [as he walks closer to Frigga she strikes him in the face with her sword, he takes out his blade and starts fighting with Frigga, she puts up a good fight but Algrim comes to his aid and subdues her, Malekith walks towards Jane] You have taken something, child. Give it back. [Malekith stands in front of Jane and as he goes to grab her she disappears and he realizes that she's a hologram, he turns to Frigga] Witch! Where is the Aether?

Name: Frigga
Line: I'll never tell.

Name: Malekith
Line: I believe you. [suddenly Algrim stabs Frigga in the back, at the same time Thor rushes in and shoots a lightning bolt at Malekith's face, severely scarring it, he and Algrim escape and jump onto their ship before Thor can catch them; after Malekith and Algrim escape Odin arrives to find Frigga dead, he holds her body in his arms as Thor and Jane look on, a funeral is held for Frigga where all the Asgardians mourn her as her body is pushed out to the sea on a boat and the boat burnt by a flaming arrow, at the same time Loki expresses his grief in his cell] [back on Earth Erik has been institutionalized and is trying to explain the convergence to the patients in his ward]

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: The universe rotates on a five thousand year cycle, and once its cycled all the worlds align. [he picks up a shoe and holds it up] Imagine...imagine that this is our world, and...and... [one of the patients hands him another shoe] Oh, thank you. And this is another world. Normally they're separate, but during the alignment everything is connected. All Nine Realms, all Nine Realms are passing through each other and gravity, light, and even matter, is crunching from one world to the other. [he demonstrates with the shoes by smacking one on top of the other repeatedly] But if this happens to us now, the result would be cataclysmic. [he then puts the shoes down and picks up two pencils and holds them up] My gravimetric spikes can stabilize the focal point of the Convergence. [he puts the pencil down and picks up the shoes again] This time the alignment, and all the other worlds, would just pass up by. It's beautiful. It's simple. Any questions? [we see the patients in the ward just carrying on with their activity, no one has really taken any notice of him, then one of the patients (Stan Lee) interrupts]

Name: Thor
Line: She's your prisoner now? [to Fandral, Volstagg and the guards] Leave us. [they all start walking off and leave Thor with Odin]

Name: Odin
Line: I do not wish to fight with you.

Name: Thor
Line: Nor I with you, but I intend to pursue Malekith.

Name: Odin
Line: We possess the Aether, Malekith will come to us.

Name: Thor
Line: Yes, and you will destroy us.

Name: Odin
Line: You overestimate the power of these creatures.

Name: Thor
Line: No, I value our peoples lives. I'll take Jane to the Dark World and draw the enemy away from Asgard. When Malekith pulls the Aether from Jane it will be exposed vulnerable, and I will destroy it and him.

Name: Odin
Line: If you fail, you risk this weapon falling into the hands of our enemies.

Name: Thor
Line: The risk is far greater if we do nothing. His ship could be over our heads right now and we'd never even know it.

Name: Odin
Line: If and when he comes, his men will fall by ten thousand Asgardian blades.

Name: Thor
Line: And how of our men shall fall on theirs?

Name: Odin
Line: As many as are needed! [there's a moment pause] We will fight! Until the last Asgardian breath, the last drop of Asgardian blood.

Name: Thor
Line: And how are you different from Malekith? [Odin chuckles]

Name: Odin
Line: The difference, my son, is that I will win. [Odin turns and walks off] [back on Earth, Darcy paces around her apartment as Ian is sat watching the news on TV]

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Jane isn't called me back. Erik isn't calling me back. Stupid SHIELD isn't calling me back!

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: What's SHIELD?

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: It's a secret. [Darcy leaves a voice message for Erik] Uh...hey, Erik. It's Darcy again. Uh...Thor came back, he took Jane to Asgard and um...I'm not sure what I'm supposed to do. [as Ian is watching the news they start reporting about Erik being arrested at Stonehenge]

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: Darcy, you really need to look at this. Your friend Erik, what was his last name again? [Darcy looks at the news report on TV]

Name: Thor
Line: You're not in Odin's war council?

Name: Heimdall
Line: The Bifrost is closed by your father's orders. No one is to come or to go. [Heimdall takes off his helmet and places it on the table] We face an enemy that is invisible even to me. Of what use is a guardian such as that? [he sits down looking defeated]

Name: Thor
Line: Malekith will return, you know this. I'll need your help.

Name: Heimdall
Line: I cannot overrule my King's wishes, not even for you.

Name: Thor
Line: I'm not asking you to. The Realms need their All-Father strong and unchallenged, whether he is or not. But he is blinded, Heimdall, by hatred and by grief.

Name: Heimdall
Line: As are we all.

Name: Thor
Line: Well I see clearly enough.

Name: Heimdall
Line: The risks are too great.

Name: Thor
Line: Everything that we do from here on is a risk, there is no other way. [Heimdall hesitates before replying]

Name: Heimdall
Line: What do you require of me?

Name: Thor
Line: What I'm about to ask of you is treason of the highest order. Success will bring us exile and failure shall mean our death. Malekith knew the Aether was here, he can sense its power. If we do nothing he will come for it again, but this time lay waste to all of Asgard. [we see Thor holding a meeting with Sif, Fandral, Volstagg and Heimdall] We must move Jane off world.

Name: Sif
Line: The Bifrost has been shut down and the Tesseract locked away in a vault.

Name: Heimdall
Line: There are other paths off Asgard, ways known only to a few.

Name: Thor
Line: One, actually. [the others suddenly realize he means Loki]

Name: Loki
Line: Thor, after all this time and now you come to visit me. Why? Have you come to gloat? To mock?

Name: Thor
Line: Loki, enough. No more illusions. [suddenly Loki's cell is transformed, the illusion is lifted and we see that Loki's cell is a mess, everything has been thrown around and he's sat on the floor, looking unkempt and messy, in the other corner of the cell]

Name: Loki
Line: Now you see me, brother. [Thor walks up to the other side of the cell to be closer to Loki] Did she suffer?

Name: Thor
Line: I did not come here to share our grief. Instead I offer you the chance of a far richer sacrament.

Name: Loki
Line: Go on.

Name: Thor
Line: I know you seek vengeance as much as I do. You help me escape Asgard and I will grant it to you, vengeance. And afterward, this cell. [Loki chuckles]

Name: Loki
Line: You must be truly desperate to come to me for help. What makes you think you can trust me?

Name: Thor
Line: I don't. Mother did. You should know that when we fought each other in the past, I did so with a glimmer of hope that my brother was still in there somewhere. That hope no longer exists to protect you. You betray me and I will kill you. [Loki smiles]

Name: Loki
Line: Hmm. When do we start? [back to the meeting with Thor and his comrades]

Name: Thor
Line: He will try. [Loki and Thor walk out of the Asgardian prison]

Name: Loki
Line: This is so unlike you, brother. So clandestine. Are you sure you wouldn't rather just punch your way out?

Name: Thor
Line: If you keep speaking I just might.

Name: Loki
Line: Fine. As you wish. I'm not even here. [using his diversion tactics Loki turns himself into an Asgardian guard] Is this better?

Name: Loki
Line: Still, we could be less conspicuous. [Loki turns back into himself but turns Thor into Sif] Hm, brother. You look ravishing. [Thor looks down at his body then replies in his own voice]

Name: Thor
Line: It will hurt no less when I kill you in this form.

Name: Loki
Line: Very well. Perhaps you prefer one of your new companions, given that you seem to like them so much. [Loki then turns himself into Captain America in his full Captain America costume] Oh, this is much better. Woh. The costume's a bit much, so tight. But the confidence, I can feel the righteousness surging. Hey, you wanna have a rousing discussion about truth, honor, patriotism? God bless Amer– [suddenly Thor grabs hold of Loki puts his hand over his mouth and pushes him against the wall making Loki turn back into himself] What? [Thor looks to the side and they see two Asgardian guards walking away] You could at least furnish me with a weapon. My dagger, something! [Thor looks at him and we hear a noise like a sword being drawn] At last, a little common sense. [Loki then looks down then holds up his hands which now have iron handcuffs on them]

Name: Thor
Line: And I thought you liked tricks. [Thor laughs and turns to walk off] [back at the original meeting Thor was holding with his comrades]

Name: Thor
Line: I won't be the one who comes for her. [Thor looks over to Sif; then we see Jane is sat in her guarded room when one of the guards enters]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: I'm not hungry. [suddenly Sif comes up behind the guard and knocks him out, she looks over to Jane]

Name: Sif
Line: Good, let's go. [Jane and Sif meet up with Thor with Loki standing beside him, Jane points to Loki]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: You're...

Name: Loki
Line: I'm Loki. You may have heard of... [suddenly Jane slaps Loki hard in the face]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: That was for New York. [Loki smiles and looks at Thor]

Name: Loki
Line: I like her. [back at Thor's meeting with his comrades]

Name: Sif
Line: And what of the All-Father?

Name: Heimdall
Line: It is my sworn duty to notify him of crimes against the throne. [Odin visits Heimdall accompanied by some of his guards]

Name: Odin
Line: You called me here on an urgent matter. What is it?

Name: Heimdall
Line: Treason, my lord.

Name: Odin
Line: Whose?

Name: Heimdall
Line: Mine. [Heimdall draws his sword, at the same time more guards interrupt them]

Name: Odin
Line: Stop Thor, by any means necessary. [as they hear the guards approaching]

Name: Sif
Line: I'll hold them off. Take her.

Name: Thor
Line: Thank you. [Thor and Jane go off, as Loki goes to follow them Sif draws her sword and places it under Loki's throat]

Name: Sif
Line: Betray him and I'll kill you. [Loki chuckles]

Name: Loki
Line: It's good to see you too, Sif. [Loki leaves to join Thor and Jane as the guards get closer to Sif; back at the original meeting with Thor and his comrades]

Name: Thor
Line: That, my friend, is where we won't be leaving by foot. [Thor, Loki and Jane meet Volstagg where Malekith's ship had crashed into the palace]

Name: Thor
Line: Thank you, my friend. [as they walk towards Malekith's crashed ship, Jane smiles and nods at Volstagg, then as Loki is about to follow Thor and Jane Volstagg stops him]

Name: Loki
Line: You'll kill me? Evidently there will be a line. [Volstagg then lets him pass] [Thor, Jane and Loki board Malekith's crashed ship, Thor looks at the controls and starts pressing some button, looking unsure of what he's doing] I thought you said you knew how to fly this thing.

Name: Thor
Line: I said, "how hard could it be?" [meanwhile, the Asgardian guards rush towards the ship with Volstagg standing guard in front of it]

Name: Loki
Line: They're on the ship! [as they approach the ship Volstagg starts attacking them; back in the ship] Well, whatever you're doing, brother, I suggest you do it faster.

Name: Thor
Line: Shut up, Loki. [outside the ship Volstagg continues to battle with the Asgardian guards; back in the ship Thor continues to frantically press every button to start the ship]

Name: Loki
Line: You must have missed something.

Name: Thor
Line: No, I didn't, I'm pressing every button on this thing.

Name: Loki
Line: No, don't hit it, just press it gently. [as he hits the buttons]

Name: Thor
Line: I am pressing it gently. It's not working! [suddenly the ship comes to life, Thor laughs; outside the ship Volstagg is overrun by the guards.]

Name: Loki
Line: I think you missed a column.

Name: Thor
Line: Shut up! [finally the ship breaks through the palace walls and takes off] [as they are flying through Asgard]

Name: Loki
Line: Look, why don't you let me take over, I'm clearly the better pilot.

Name: Thor
Line: Is that right? Well, out of the two of us which one can actually fly? [as they are flying over Asgard suddenly Jane collapses]

Name: Loki
Line: Oh, dear. Is she dead?

Name: Thor
Line: Jane. [Jane raises her head, looking weak]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: I'm okay. [as they continue to fly, the ship hits and breaks off a part of a massive building; to Loki]

Name: Thor
Line: Not a word. [several smaller Asgardian ships start following them]

Name: Loki
Line: Now they're following us. [the smaller ships start firing at them] Now they're firing at us!

Name: Thor
Line: Yeah, thank you for the commentary, Loki! It's not at all distracting! [the ship then hits a massive stone monument of King Bor, breaking the head off]

Name: Loki
Line: Well done, you just decapitated your grandfather. [the smaller ships continue to follow and fire at them as they fly over Asgard] You know this is wonderful. This is a tremendous idea. Let's steal the biggest, most obvious ship in the universe and escape in that. Flying around the city, smashing into everything in sight so everyone can see us. It's brilliant, Thor! It's truly brilliant! [suddenly Thor pushes Loki off the ship, Thor then picks up Jane and jumps off the flying ship and lands onto a smaller ship being flown by Fandral, Loki has also fallen onto the ship]

Name: Loki
Line: You lied to me. I'm impressed.

Name: Thor
Line: I'm glad you're pleased. Now, do as you promised. Take us to your secret pathway. [Loki smiles and takes over the ship's control, at the same time the Asgardian ships spot them and start firing at them] Fandral.

Name: Thor
Line: Loki!

Name: Loki
Line: If it were easy everyone would do it.

Name: Thor
Line: Are you mad?

Name: Loki
Line: Possibly. [Thor holds on to Jane, as Loki heads straight for the wall of the mountain, suddenly they enter right through the mountain and then enter through a portal to Svartalfheim] Ta-da! [on their ship, Algrim approaches Malekith]

Name: Malekith
Line: [subtitled] No. Asgard is not important anymore. The Aether has returned home. [as they fly over Svartalfheim, Jane continues to lie down and Thor puts a cover over her]

Name: Loki
Line: [sighs] What I could do with the power that flows through those veins.

Name: Thor
Line: It would consume you.

Name: Loki
Line: She's holding up alright, for now.

Name: Thor
Line: She's strong in ways you'd never even know.

Name: Loki
Line: Say goodbye.

Name: Thor
Line: Not this day.

Name: Loki
Line: This day, the next, a hundred years, it's nothing. It's a heart beat. You'll never be ready. The only woman whose love you've prized will be snatched from you.

Name: Thor
Line: And will that satisfy you?

Name: Loki
Line: Satisfaction is not in my nature.

Name: Thor
Line: Surrender not in mine.

Name: Loki
Line: The son of Odin.

Name: Thor
Line: No, not just of Odin! You think you alone were loved of mother? You had her tricks, but I had her trust!

Name: Loki
Line: Trust. Was that her last expression? Trust? When you let her die!

Name: Thor
Line: What help were you in your cell?

Name: Loki
Line: Who put me there? Who put me there?! [Thor grabs hold of Loki]

Name: Thor
Line: You know damn well! You know damn well who! [Thor raises his fist to punch Loki but stops himself] She wouldn't want us to fight.

Name: Loki
Line: Well, she wouldn't exactly be shocked. [they both smile]

Name: Thor
Line: I wish I could trust you. [Thor turns his back to Loki]

Name: Loki
Line: Trust my rage. [back on Earth, Darcy and Ian go to free Erik from the mental institution]

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: What? Oh, yeah. My father, Dr. Erik Selvig. [Ian goes to sign the form]

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Erik.

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: Yeah, those. Thank goodness. [as Erik comes towards Darcy]

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Erik.

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: Yes?

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: It's uh...Darcy.

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: Darcy. [Darcy holds up her hands and smiles, Erik then hugs her] It's so good to see you.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Uh...I missed you too. [Darcy looks awkward as Erik continues to hold her tightly]

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: How did you find me?

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: You were naked on TV.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Okay, time to go. Lots to do. [Erik continues to hold her] Getting weird now. [as they walk down the corridor of the mental institution with Ian holding Erik's gadgets] I should not be left in charge of stuff like this, I don't get paid enough. I don't get paid period. [Erik takes his bag of medicine from Ian]

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: I'm uh...Ian by the way. Uh..Darcy's intern. I don't get paid either. [Ian watches as Erik takes out a bottle of pills] Are you alright?

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: I have had a God in my brain. I don't recommend it. [as they step out of the building suddenly the gadget in Ian arms starts to beep]

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: Dr. Selvig, your gear is beeping at me.

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: It's happening, sooner than I calculated.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Wait, what's happening? [they look up to see flock of birds flying above them] Birds? Birds are happening?

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: They're starlings, it's called a murmuration. My dad used to take me bird watching as a kid.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Erik?

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: Look. [suddenly the birds all fly in the same direction and they all suddenly disappear]

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Where did they go? [suddenly all the birds appear behind, them flying away frantically making Darcy screams in terror] What the hell was that?! [Erik smiles] Why are you smiling?

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: There's nothing more reassuring than realizing that the world is crazier than you are. [he walks ahead and throws his bag of medicine into the garbage bin nearby] Take me to Jane's lab! [on Svartalfheim, as they continue flying on their ship suddenly Jane's eyes open, it's clear that the Aether has taken her over, she rises and looks ahead]

Name: Thor
Line: Jane.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Malekith. [after landing their ship, they walk over to watch Malekith and his men in the distance]

Name: Thor
Line: Alright, are you ready? [Jane nods her head]

Name: Loki
Line: I am. [they rise from their hiding spot and Malekith spots them standing on a hill in the distance] You know this plan of yours is going to get us killed.

Name: Thor
Line: Yeah, possibly. [Loki holds up his shackled hands for Thor to uncuff him]

Name: Loki
Line: You still don't trust me, brother?

Name: Thor
Line: Would you? [Thor takes off Loki's cuffs]

Name: Loki
Line: No, I wouldn't. [suddenly Loki takes out a dagger stabs Thor and throws him down the hill]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Thor! No! [Malekith sees this and starts walking towards them] [after stabbing Thor and throwing him down the hill, Loki walks over to Thor]

Name: Loki
Line: You really think I cared about Frigga, about any of you? [he kicks Thor in the stomach] All I ever wanted was you and Odin dead at my feet! [Thor raises his hand, attempting to summon Mjolnir, but Loki cuts off his hand making Thor scream out in pain, Jane rushes over to Thor but Loki grabs her and turns to face Malekith and his dark elves] Malekith, I am Loki of Jotunheim and I bring you a gift! [he throws Jane at Malekith's feet] I ask only one thing in return, a good seat from which to watch Asgard burn.

Name: Malekith
Line: Look at me. [Malekith uses his foot to turn Thor, he then lifts Jane in the air and extracts the Aether from her, in that moment Jane has a vision of Earth, then as the Aether leaves her body Jane falls to the ground]

Name: Thor
Line: Loki, now! [Loki uses his diversion tactics and we see that he had never amputated Thor's hand, Thor quickly summons Mjolnir and shoots lightning at the Aether attempting to destroy it, but he fails as Malekith is still able to absorb it and turns to leave on his ship] [two of the dark elves start attacking Thor but he quickly takes them down, Algrim then throws one of his vortex weapons in the air, Loki pushes Jane away and he is nearly sucked in when Thor pulls him out, Thor then attacks Algrim but he beats Thor down, Loki goes over to them and impales Algrim from behind, Algrim slowly turns and suddenly pulls Loki into the blade that is sticking out from him] No! [Algrim takes a step towards Loki]

Name: Loki
Line: See you in hell, monster! [Algrim then realizes that attached to the blade in him is his own vortex weapon, it explodes before he can do anything destroying him; Thor then rushes over to Loki]

Name: Thor
Line: No. No, no, no! Oh, you fool, you didn't listen!

Name: Loki
Line: I know. I'm a fool. I'm a fool! [Loki squirms in pain]

Name: Thor
Line: Stay with me, okay?

Name: Loki
Line: I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

Name: Thor
Line: Shh.

Name: Loki
Line: I'm sorry.

Name: Thor
Line: It's okay. [Thor nods his head] It's alright. I'll tell father what you did here today.

Name: Loki
Line: I didn't do it for him. [he closes his eyes and as he dies his skin turns to it's blue Frost Giant form, Thor cries out in anguish]

Name: Thor
Line: No! [Thor looks at Jane as he weeps for Loki] [after Loki's death, Thor and Jane enter a cave as they see a storm approaching]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: He's gonna unleash it, not just on Asgard or on a star, Malekith is gonna destroy everything.

Name: Thor
Line: How? Jane, how?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: I saw him on Earth. Why would he go to Earth?

Name: Thor
Line: The Convergence.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Oh, God. None of this would have happened if I hadn't found the Aether.

Name: Thor
Line: Then Malekith would have only possessed it that much sooner.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: I only found it because I was looking for you.

Name: Thor
Line: Jane. [he places his hand on her face]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Now we're trapped here. [suddenly they hear music playing, Jane and Thor look at each other in confusion]

Name: Thor
Line: It's not me. [Jane realizes it's her cell phone, she takes it out of her pocket and answers it]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Hello?

Name: Richard
Line: Hi, Jane, it's Richard.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Richard?! Where are you?

Name: Richard
Line: I'm still in the office. It's...It's been a crazy day here today. [Jane puts him on speaker and holds up her phone]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Oh, my God! This is amazing.

Name: Richard
Line: Is it? I quite enjoyed our lunch despite never actually ordering anything.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: How am I getting service here?

Name: Richard
Line: Is this a bad time? Do you want me to try you there?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: No, no, no, no! Please, whatever you do, do not hang up the phone.

Name: Richard
Line: Okay then. I was just wondering if you want to try again? Uh...maybe dinner next time.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Uh...yeah, yeah, yeah. Um...just stay on the phone, okay?

Name: Richard
Line: Yeah, I will. [Jane looks down and notices can and keys that were thrown through from the abandoned factory]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Oh, my God. [Jane picks up the keys from the floor of the cave]

Name: Richard
Line: Am I interrupting something.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: No, no, no, nothing at all. [realizing how they can return to Earth, Jane turns to Thor] Come on.

Name: Richard
Line: I'm losing you there, are you in a tunnel? [Thor starts following Jane]

Name: Thor
Line: Where are we going?

Name: Richard
Line: [to Jane] Hello? [they start walking further into the cave, Thor notices the discarded shoes that were thrown through from the abandoned factory]

Name: Thor
Line: Why are there so many shoes in here? [as they walks further in suddenly they disappear; back in his office Richard loses Jane on the phone]

Name: Richard
Line: I'll just text her. [Jane and Thor appear back on Earth outside the factory, they get into Ian's abandoned car still parked outside the factory and Jane tries to start the car]

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Jane!

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Hey.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: You can't just leave like that, the whole world is going crazy! [Thor hangs his hammer on the coat hanger next to the door] All the stuff we saw is spreading. [she looks at Jane's Asgardian clothes and disheveled state] Did you go to a party? [Jane notices Erik for the first time]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Erik?!

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: Jane, how wonderful! [he rises and goes to Jane and as he embraces her we see he isn't wearing any pants] You've been to Asgard.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Where are your pants?

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: Oh, uh...he uh...he says it helps him think.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Okay. Well, I'm gonna need everything you got on this. All the work you've been doing on gravimetric anomalies, everything.

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: Okay.

Name: Thor
Line: Are you well, Erik? [Erik chuckles then his smile fades quickly]

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: Your brother is not coming, is he?

Name: Thor
Line: Loki is dead.

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: Oh, thank God. [Thor looks at him in confusion] I...I'm so sorry.

Name: Thor
Line: Thank you. [Erik then embraces Thor] [back on Svartalfheim we see an Einherjar Guard use the ship that brought Thor, Loki and Jane onto the planet to return to Asgard, he goes to see Odin at the palace]

Name: Odin
Line: Thor?

Name: Odin
Line: What?

Name: Odin
Line: Loki. [the warrior doesn't reply but just looks at Odin] [back at Jane's apartment]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Malekith is going to fire the Aether at a spot where all the nine worlds are connected.

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: Amplifying the weapon's impact. With each additional world, the power will increase exponentially. The effect would be universal.

Name: Thor
Line: Yes, well the alignment is only temporary. He must be in exactly at the right place at the right time.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Well, how do we know where that is?

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: We follow the directions. This has happened before, thousands of years ago, and The Ancients were there to see it. [Erik places a map of the British Isles on the coffee table] All the great constructions

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: Greenwich?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: The walls between worlds will be almost non-existent. Physics is gonna go ballistic. Increase and decrease in gravity, spatial extrusions. The very fabric of reality is gonna be torn apart. [Thor summons Mjolnir and it shoots over to Thor's hand from the where it was hanging on the coat hanger]

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: I better get my pants. [in Greenwich at the location outside a library Darcy and Ian grab Erik's gadget]

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Focus, this is important. We have to hammer them in all around the site and then Jane and Erik will activate them from the tower.

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: They're taped together!

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Do you even know what these things do?

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: No.

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Neither do I. [Darcy and Ian start placing Erik's gadgets around the library grounds] Come on, come on!

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: Fine! [suddenly Malekith's giant ship appears on the River Thames near the library grounds]

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Holy shit! [the ship starts moving forward and crashing through the library grounds causing pandemonium until it finally stops in the middle of the grounds, Malekith and his dark elves step off the ship and the same time Thor flies in and lands in front of Malekith]

Name: Malekith
Line: You needn't have come so far, Asgardian! Death would have come to you soon enough.

Name: Thor
Line: Not by your hand!

Name: Malekith
Line: Your universe was never meant to be. Your world and your family will be extinguished. [Malekith uses the power of the Aether to attack Thor but Thor manages to narrowly miss getting hit by it] [inside the library setting up the gravimetric device]

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: We're running out of time.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Almost there.

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: Are you sure this is going to work? These devices were made to detect anomalies, not cause them.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Oh, come on. [Jane looks out and sees Thor and Malekith battling it out] Come on, Darcy. [Jane rushes off to find Darcy; outside Thor manages to deflect the Aether that Malekith is using to fight him off]

Name: Thor
Line: You know with all that power, I thought you would hit harder. [as Malekith is using the Aether to shield himself suddenly Thor throws his hammer at him which throws Malekith across the ground and smashes him against the library building, at the same time Jane sees Darcy and Ian placing the last of Erik's device in the ground]

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: Done. [Darcy gives the OK sign to Jane and Jane rushes back to Erik]

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: The Convergence will be in full effect in seven minutes.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: That just means we have to keep Malekith busy for eight. [Jane gets the device ready] Okay, you might wanna hold on to something. [she turns on the device and suddenly some of the dark elves suddenly disappear; Darcy and Ian watch this nearby, Darcy talks to Jane on her phone]

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: That is awesome! How did you do that?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Well, gravitational fields interact with the weak spot between worlds creating...

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Oh, there's a guy with a sword! [Jane uses the device again to make the dark elf disappear but instead she accidentally makes Darcy and Ian disappear]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Oops.

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: Let's go. [Darcy and Ian appear in another part of London]

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: What the hell just happened? [suddenly the dark elves that had also disappeared appear and fall onto a parked car] Move! [Darcy grabs hold of Ian's hand and they run off as the dark elves start chasing after them; back at the library Thor and Malekith continue their battle and everyone inside the library rushes to the windows to watch]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: What are you all doing? You need to get out of here! Now!

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: What are you doing?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: My signal's lost connection. [some of the dark elves are behind them chasing after them]

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: Jane! Come on! [as Thor and Malekith continue their battle through the realms they land in Jotunheim and are confronted by a giant beast which then is transported to London, at the same time Darcy and Ian are being ambushed by the dark elves when Ian, with the help of the anti-gravitational energy force, grabs a car and throws it at them, Darcy looks at him in shock]

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: Are you alright?

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: You saved my life.

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: Yeah. Yes, I did. [back at the library grounds Jane manages to make the device work again and as she uses it suddenly makes Darcy and Ian appear behind her in each others arms kissing]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Darcy?

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Jane! [Darcy lets go of Ian and falls to the ground]

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: Ian?

Name: Ian Boothby
Line: Selvig! [suddenly Mjolnir appears and flies past them]

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: Meowmeow! [Thor and Malekith are then transported through the realms again with Malekith landing back in Greenwich but Thor ends up in Charing Cross Underground Station]

Name: Thor
Line: How do I get to Greenwich?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: We're out of time. [Jane rushes off ahead]

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: Jane. Jane! [Thor rushes out of the station to watch the Aether taking over]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Thor! We're too late.

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: The Convergence is at its peak. [Thor looks at the gadget spears in Erik's hand]

Name: Thor
Line: Can those things stop him?

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: Not from here.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: We can't get close enough. [Thor looks at Jane]

Name: Thor
Line: I can. [Thor takes the spears from Erik and rushes off towards Malekith] [Thor pushes through the Aether and reaches Malekith] Malekith! [Malekith turns to face Thor]

Name: Malekith
Line: Darkness returns, Asgardian. Have you come to witness the end of your universe?

Name: Thor
Line: I've come to accept your surrender. [Thor throws one of Erik's gadget spears at Malekith and he catches it, Jane uses the gavemetric which makes his arm disappear and we see it transported to Svartalfheim, Thor throws the other spear at Malekith and he catches it and his other arm disappears]

Name: Malekith
Line: You think you can stop this? The Aether cannot be destroyed.

Name: Thor
Line: But you can. [Thor summons Mjolnir at the same time he rushes towards Malekith and as he grabs his hammer he uses it to throw Malekith into his ship and Jane is able to use her device to transport him Svartalfheim] [after Thor kills Malekith Jane goes to find Thor and finds him lying on the ground, suddenly Malekith's ship starts to crumble, Jane rushes towards the unconscious Thor]

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Thor! No! [Jane turns Thor over grabs his arm and starts to pull him out of the way but he is too heavy, just them Erik, Darcy and Ian arrive on the scene]

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: Jane! [the ship starts to fall, as Jane is not able to move Thor she throws herself on top of him and holds on to him with her eyes closed, just as the ship is about to land on them it disappears and appears on Svartalfheim landing on Malekith and crushing him to death; back in Greenwich] Everybody okay? [Thor becomes conscious and opens his eyes, Darcy smiles and throws her arms around Ian and kisses him passionately] [couple of days later, Jane, Erik, Darcy and Ian are in her apartment sat having breakfast quietly]

Name: Darcy Lewis
Line: He's gonna come back. Except, you know, last time he was gone for, like, two years.

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Well, it's only been two days, so...

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: Did he say anything before he left?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Yeah, he had to figure some stuff out with his father. He kind of committed treason... on our way out. [Jane looks away and carries on eating her breakfast]

Name: Erik Selvig
Line: Oh.

Name: Odin
Line: You once said there would never be a wiser King than me. You were wrong. The alignment has brought all the realms together. Every one of them saw you offer your life to save them. What can Asgard offer its new King in return?

Name: Thor
Line: My life. Father, I cannot be King of Asgard. I will protect Asgard and all the realms with my last and every breath, but I cannot do so from that chair. Loki, for all his grave imbalance, understood rule as I know I never will. The brutality, the sacrifice, it changes you. I'd rather be a good man than a great King.

Name: Odin
Line: Is this my son I hear, or the woman he loves?

Name: Thor
Line: When you speak, do I never hear Mother's voice? [Odin sighs] This is not for Jane, Father. She does not know what I came here to say. Now forbid me to see her or say she can rule at my side, it changes nothing.

Name: Odin
Line: One son who wanted the throne too much, another who will not take it. Is this my legacy?

Name: Thor
Line: Loki died with honor, I shall try to live the same. Is that not legacy enough? [Odin nods his head, Thor then holds up Mjolnir to offer it back to Odin]

Name: Odin
Line: It belongs to you, if you are worthy of it.

Name: Thor
Line: I shall try to be.

Name: Odin
Line: I cannot give you my blessing, nor can I wish you good fortune.

Name: Thor
Line: I know. [Thor turns to leave]

Name: Odin
Line: If I were proud of the man my son had become, even that I could not say. It would speak only from my heart. Go, my son. [Thor smiles]

Name: Thor
Line: Thank you, father. [he turns and starts walking off, as Odin watches Thor walk off Odin's form transform to reveal Loki]

Name: Loki
Line: No. Thank you. [Loki smiles devilishly] [mid-credits scene; Sif and Volstagg are taken to meet, The Collector Taneleer Tivan]

Name: Sif
Line: You know why we're here.

Name: Sif
Line: See that it is. [The Collector bows his head, Sif and Volstagg turn and leave]

Name: Sif
Line: I've got this completely under control!

Name: Thor
Line: Is that why everything's on fire?

Name: Sif
Line: All yours. [steps back]

Name: Thor
Line: Hello. [the beast roars] I accept your surrender.

Name: Thor
Line: Anyone else?

Name: Loki
Line: [mock salute to Odin] I really don't see what all the fuss is about…

Name: Odin
Line: Do you not truly feel the gravity of your crimes? Wherever you go there is war, ruin and death!

Name: Loki
Line: I went down to Midgard to rule the people of Earth as a benevolent God, just like you.

Name: Odin
Line: We are not gods. We're born, we live, we die, just as humans do.

Name: Loki
Line: Give or take five thousand years.

Name: Odin
Line: All this because Loki desires a throne...

Name: Loki
Line: It is my birthright!

Name: Odin
Line: Your birthright was to DIE! As a child, cast out on a frozen rock. If I had not taken you in, you would not be here now, to hate me.

Name: Loki
Line: If I'm for the axe, then for mercy's sake, just swing it. It's not that I don't like our little talks, it's just... I don't love them.

Name: Odin
Line: Frigga is the only reason you're still alive, and you will never see her again. You'll spend the rest of your days in the dungeons.

Name: Loki
Line: And what of Thor? You'll make that witless oaf King while I rot in chains?

Name: Odin
Line: Thor must strive to undo the damage you have done. He will bring order to the Nine Realms, and then, yes, he will be King.

Name: Thor
Line: Jane?

Name: Jane Foster
Line: Sorry. I just…needed to make sure you were real. It's been a very strange day.

Name: Thor
Line: I am. Jane—

Name: Thor
Line: Where were you? Heimdall could not see you.

Name: Thor
Line: I know. I know, but the Bifröst was destroyed. The Nine Realms erupted into chaos. Wars were raging, marauders were pillaging…I had to put an end to the slaughter.

Name: Thor
Line: Jane, I fought to protect you from the dangers of my world, but I was wrong. I was a fool. I believe that fate brought us together.

Name: Malekith
Line: [looking out over the ruins of Svartalfheim] Look upon my legacy, Algrim. I can barely remember a time before the light.

Name: Malekith
Line: The Asgardians will suffer as we have suffered. I will reclaim the Aether. I will restore our world. And I will put an end to this poisoned universe.

Name: Odin
Line: She does not belong in Asgard any more than a goat belongs at a banquet!

Name: Odin
Line: I am Odin. King of Asgard. Protector of the Nine Realms.

Name: Odin
Line: I know very well who you are, Jane Foster.

Name: Frigga
Line: You know full well it was your actions that brought you here.

Name: Loki
Line: My actions? I was merely giving truth to the lie that I had been fed my entire life…that I was born to be a king.

Name: Frigga
Line: A king? A true king admits his faults. What of the lives you took on Earth?

Name: Loki
Line: A mere handful compared to the number that Odin has taken himself.

Name: Frigga
Line: Your father—

Name: Loki
Line: He's not my father!

Name: Frigga
Line: Then am I not your mother?

Name: Loki
Line: You're not.

Name: Frigga
Line: [looks hurt but chuckles] You're always so perceptive about everyone but yourself. [Loki looks sorry and reaches for her but she disappears]

Name: Frigga
Line: Stand down, creature, and you may still survive this.

Name: Malekith
Line: I have survived worse, woman.

Name: Frigga
Line: Who are you?

Name: Malekith
Line: I am Malekith... [looks at Jane] and I would have what is mine. [They both draw swords and duel, until Algrim arrives and helps overpower Frigga. Malekith turns to confront Jane] You have taken something, child. Give it back. [Malekith discovers Jane is an illusion and angrily faces a grinning Frigga] WITCH! Where is the Aether?!

Name: Frigga
Line: I'll never tell you.

Name: Malekith
Line: I believe you. [Algrim kills Frigga]

Name: Loki
Line: Thor. After all this time and now you come to visit me. Why? Have you come to gloat? To mock?

Name: Thor
Line: Loki, enough. No more illusions. [Loki and the neat room turn to a destroyed room with Loki looking disheveled on the floor]

Name: Loki
Line: Now you see me, brother. Did she suffer? [referring to Frigga]

Name: Thor
Line: I did not come here to share our grief. Instead, I offer you the chance of a far richer sacrament.

Name: Loki
Line: Go on.

Name: Thor
Line: I know you seek vengeance as much as I do. You help me escape Asgard, and I will grant it to you. Vengeance. And afterward, this cell.

Name: Loki
Line: [chuckles] You must be truly desperate to come to me for help. What makes you think you can trust me?

Name: Thor
Line: I don't. Mother did. You should know that when we fought each other in the past, I did so with a glimmer of hope that my brother was still in there somewhere. That hope no longer exists to protect you. You betray me, and I will kill you.

Name: Loki
Line: Hm. When do we start?

Name: Loki
Line: I'm Loki. You may have heard—

Name: Loki
Line: [to Thor] I like her.

Name: Sif
Line: Betray him, and I'll kill you.

Name: Loki
Line: Good to see you too, Sif.

Name: Loki
Line: You'll kill me? Evidently, there will be a line.

Name: Loki
Line: You know, this is wonderful! This a tremendous idea! Let's steal the biggest, most obvious ship in the universe and escape in that! Flying around the city, smash it into everything in sight so everyone can see us! It's brilliant, Thor! It's truly brilliant- [Thor shoves Loki out of the ship, and jumps out with Jane in his arms into a skiff piloted by Fandral]

Name: Loki
Line: [to Thor] You lied to me. I'm impressed.

Name: Loki
Line: [steering the skiff towards a tiny crevice in the mountain] If it were easy, everyone would do it.

Name: Thor
Line: Are you mad?

Name: Loki
Line: Possibly.

Name: Thor
Line: You think you alone were loved of Mother? You had her tricks, but I had her trust!

Name: Loki
Line: Trust? Was that her last expression, trust? While you let her die?!

Name: Thor
Line: What good were you in your cell?

Name: Loki
Line: Who put me there? Who put me there?!

Name: Thor
Line: You know damn well! You know damn well who! [pins Loki and is about to hit him but lets him go] She wouldn't want us to fight.

Name: Loki
Line: Well, she wouldn't exactly be shocked.

Name: Thor
Line: [chuckles] I wish I could trust you.

Name: Loki
Line: [whispers] Trust my rage.

Name: Thor
Line: [holding a dying Loki] I will tell Father what you did here today.

Name: Loki
Line: I didn't do it for him.

Name: Malekith
Line: You needn't have come so far, Asgardian. Death would have come to you soon enough.

Name: Thor
Line: Not by your hand!

Name: Malekith
Line: Your universe was never meant to be. Your world and your family will be EXTINGUISHED!

Name: Malekith
Line: Darkness returns, Asgardian. Have you come to witness the end of your universe?

Name: Thor
Line: I've come to accept your surrender.

Name: Malekith
Line: You think you can stop this?! The Aether cannot be destroyed!

Name: Thor
Line: But you can. [summons Mjolnir and deals the final blow to Malekith]

Name: Odin
Line: One son who wanted the throne too much, and another who will not take it. Is this my legacy?

Name: Thor
Line: Loki died with honour. I shall try to live the same. Is that not legacy enough? [offers the hammer]

Name: Odin
Line: It belongs to you, if you are worthy of it.

Name: Thor
Line: I shall try to be.

Name: Odin
Line: I can not give you my blessing, nor can I wish you good fortune.

Name: Thor
Line: I know. [turns to leave]

Name: Odin
Line: If I were proud of the man my son has become, even that I could not say, it would speak only from my heart. Go, my son.

Name: Thor
Line: Thank you, Father. [leaves]

Name: Loki
Line: [appears from Odin's guise] No... thank you.

Name: Sif
Line: You know why we're here. [she hands him the Aether, which he accepts]

Name: Sif
Line: See that it is.
